      <title>比特币减半创造新的切入点：Gazmararian</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/bitcoin-upcoming-halving-to-create-new-entry-point-token-bay-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Token Bay Capital 创始人兼管理合伙人 Lucy Gazmararian 讨论即将到来的比特币减半对市场意味着什么。减半将使该代币的新增供应量减少一半，预计在 4 月 20 日左右进行。Gazmararian 在“彭博社：中国秀”上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/bitcoin-upcoming-halving-to-create-new-entry-point-token-bay-capital</guid>
